{"tid":808272,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"傳中國使館派車接人「自認中國人可坐」 關西機場否認外車可以進入","createTime":"2018-09-06T08:07:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-07T11:21:22.000Z","uid":35790,"like":43,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"24829fad9e80524dea1c963c7820dbab1c16a9d5","tid":808272,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T08:07:02.000Z","msg":"傳陸使館派車接人「自認中國人可坐」 關西機場否認外車進入。<br />\n<br />\n關西機場營運公司在昨日一早天氣好轉後，派出巴士與高速船接駁受困民眾，因人數眾多救援作業持續到深夜。有消息稱中國大陸使館昨日派出了15輛遊覽車前往接出受困的大陸旅客，當時有台灣旅客詢問能否一起搭車？對方回答，若自認是中國人，就可上車跟祖國走！<br />\n<br />\n不過記者詢問關西機場營運公司，對方表示為了管控現場狀況，避免混亂造成更多困擾，[url]昨日全天進行管制，只有關西機場方面調度的車輛可以進入。[/url]<br />\n&lt;聯合&gt;"},{"pid":"d604b79ab263e987ebc82c17fb4c7104daad51c9","tid":808272,"uid":35790,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T08:09:39.000Z","msg":"昨日全天進行管制，只有關西機場方面調度的車輛可以進入。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"875c920ea74cb9736dda1142e6174118a3947e21","tid":808272,"uid":160662,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T08:11:15.000Z","msg":"又要入黎打起飛機先<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc346885feebf120b200706d05f3cc71ff7294b2","tid":808272,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T08:13:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28fdba2a7fd1167ab6c42ab038a44583921070f0","tid":808272,"uid":85659,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T08:14:05.000Z","msg":"睇台狗既PTT 有人衝左出黎圖文並茂作左個故仔話無呢件事WO"},{"pid":"b17c452fe98b2562f3b4b5fcb73c35a4239a3e78","tid":808272,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T08:14:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" cl