=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ace8539e2d251d96ec14f2ab11a1280c1c769678","tid":808272,"uid":50386,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T08:54:29.000Z","msg":"環時：<br />\n<br />\n總領館表示，因颱風滯留日本關西國際機場旅客總共約2650人，其中有750餘人是中國公民。總領館則第一時間啟動應急機制，派出第一批工作組趕赴關西國際機場周邊，了解被困中國旅客情況，並與日方協調對策方案，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">最終日方在今天上午啟動了集中轉運中國旅客工作</span>，分四批轉移中國旅客，其中前兩批就已轉移了360人。<br />\n<br />\n支那煩到日本要搵車專門載支那人走廢事搞到其他人<br />\n同泰國整支那專用通道異曲同工 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d3dc34cd865dd553b5a76e077bc60a7c1814ff4","tid":808272,"uid":20058,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"928e00c8d30da15335aafaf9ec60f408b2386efd","tid":808272,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"604295f20ac60662ce92704f91aea72a11c51414","tid":808272,"uid":39855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"68e19a86f34d2ab9658e39a9691f43220c869630","tid":808272,"uid":20058,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T08:20:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/128807942654/posts/10156274956317655/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F128807942654%2Fposts%2F10156274956317655%2F&d=uPgkHeRgIihchTmC1i67d0%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=5efc041f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/128807942654/posts/10156274956317655/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n車禍？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T08:40:43.000Z","msg":"唔似係機場，似係接駁位。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T08:48:03.000Z","msg":"KIX坐巴士個位係有蓋，呢個可能係臨空城"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T08:57:38.000Z","msg":"隔離有人搵到環球時報嘅原文<br />\n<br />\n係日本派車<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55f41fa0acfc2cd4f08f7caf92859503552cfb27","tid":808272,"uid":25424,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"8d3dc34cd865dd553b5a76e0